data.description: PRICE REDUCTION! Golf for free and share privileges with your guests in this active community.  Golf, tennis, clubhouse all included in your HOA.   Live  full-time in vacation mode on a quiet street in the Tri Palm Estates. Move right in and sit on your large covered patio looking out to the 6th hole of the 18 hole golf course with Eastern Mountain Views and your own grapes and orange trees. This 55 plus community has it all. Enjoy high ceilings and partial, laminate wood floors; 2 car attached garage and low HOAs ($258) that cover green fees for owners on an 18 hole and  9 hole course. Clubhouse with ''The Grill'' Restaurant, Meeting Room; 2 large pools; Jacuzzi; two Lighted Tennis courts; Shuffleboard and Pickle Ball Courts.  There is also a  section with a shallow  pool and playground for kids.  Kitchen is open to the living area.  Gas cooktop.  Solar System; inside laundry area.  Low maintenance Desert-Scape yard. New carpet in den and guest room installed first week of Nov..  Also installed new faucets in both bathrooms. Close proximity to Acrisure Ice Hockey Arena; Aqua Caliente Casino Resort Spa  and Rancho Mirage Plaza with, stores and restaurants, i.e. Walmart; Inn & Out; Costco; Chik-Fil-A; Sams Club and so many others.
